        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 19. Male ventrites of species of Anchylorhynchus. Scales: 500 µm. A A. amazonicus, showing recumbent hairs. B A. amazonicus, showing a morph with less elongate scales. C A. imitator, showing that scales on ventrites are never as elongate as in A. amazonicus. D A. goiano. E A. vittipennis. F A. variabilis." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4488009/files/figure.png" .

